# Pre-Flight Checklist

> Run this before Phase 3 (Implementation) begins.
> Every item must be checked. If any tool is missing, install it before proceeding.

## Environment
- [ ] Claude Code installed and authenticated (`claude --version`)
- [ ] AionUI installed and Claude Code detected (`brew install aionui` or download)
- [ ] Node.js 20+ (`node --version`)
- [ ] Git configured with your identity (`git config user.name && git config user.email`)
- [ ] Deployment target accessible (Coolify dashboard loads, or Vercel CLI works)

## Project Files
- [ ] CLAUDE.md exists at project root and customized for this project
- [ ] KNOWLEDGE.md exists (empty template is fine)
- [ ] TASKS.md exists with phased wave plan
- [ ] REVIEW.md exists with project-specific review rules
- [ ] .gitignore includes node_modules, .next, .env, build artifacts
- [ ] .env.example exists with all required variables documented

## Quality Gates
- [ ] Lint configured (`npm run lint` works)
- [ ] Build works (`npm run build` passes)
- [ ] Subagents copied to .claude/agents/ (architecture-enforcer, test-writer, code-reviewer, security-auditor)
- [ ] Skills symlinked from ~/.claude/skills/ (relevant skills for this project)

## Repo Legibility
- [ ] Run repo-scorer subagent — score must be 50+/70 before implementation begins
- [ ] If score < 50, fix the gaps identified in the scorecard before proceeding

## AionUI Sessions
- [ ] AionUI open with project workspace selected
- [ ] 3 sessions configured: Builder (Opus), Tester (Sonnet), Scout (Sonnet)
- [ ] MCP tools configured in AionUI (syncs to all sessions)

**All items checked? Proceed to Phase 3: Implement.**
